descriptionNullable:
It appears that you've provided a tabular data structure with various columns. Here's a description of each column in your data:

employID: An identifier for each employee or reviewer.
rating: The rating given by the reviewer, typically on a scale from 1 to 5.
reviewDate: The date on which the review was submitted.
reviewHeadLine: A brief headline or summary of the review.
authorLocation: The location or place of the author or reviewer.
Products: The type of products or services being reviewed, e.g., "Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) Implementation" or "Cybersecurity Services."
authorJobTitle: The job title or position of the author or reviewer.
pros: The positive aspects or strengths mentioned in the review.
cons: The negative aspects or weaknesses mentioned in the review.
subRatings: Sub-ratings or ratings for different aspects of the product or service, which appear to be in a list format.
authorReviewLink: A link to the author's review, if applicable.
reviewDateIST: The review date in Indian Standard Time (IST) format, including the time.
dayOfWeek: The day of the week on which the review was submitted.
month: The month in which the review was submitted.
dayOfMonth: The day of the month on which the review was submitted.
year: The year in which the review was submitted.
peher: Indicates whether the time of review is in the morning (AM) or afternoon/evening (PM).
This data seems to represent reviews or feedback from different authors or reviewers for various products or services, along with associated information such as ratings, location, job titles, and more. The data appears to be related to employee or customer reviews.
